# Quick picks

- **Best overall:** Magnesium Glycinate (200–300 mg elemental)
  <a href="https://merchant.example.com/mg-glycinate?aff=wildandwell" target="_blank" rel="nofollow sponsored noopener">Shop Glycinate →</a>

- **For focus + sleep:** Magnesium L-Threonate (dose spread earlier)
  <a href="https://merchant.example.com/mg-threonate?aff=wildandwell" target="_blank" rel="nofollow sponsored noopener">Shop Threonate →</a>

- **Budget:** Magnesium Citrate (use lower dose to avoid GI upset)
  <a href="https://merchant.example.com/mg-citrate?aff=wildandwell" target="_blank" rel="nofollow sponsored noopener">Shop Citrate →</a>

## How to use
Take with a small snack 60–90 minutes before bed. Pair with **[Blue-Light Tools](/guides/best-blue-light-tools)** for better results.

